<i>adverb</i>: 공경히 [공경히], 경건히 [경ː건히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>공경히 [공경히]</dt><br>
<dd>respectfully; reverently</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람을 공손히 받들어 모시는 마음으로.</dd><br>
<dd>With respect for the elderly.</dd><br>
<dt>경건히 [경ː건히]</dt><br>
<dd>reverently; devoutly; piously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상에 대해 공손하고 엄숙하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Respectfully and solemnly in treating someone or something.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>